00:01:36.800 --> 00:01:45.560
 University of Oregon with a thesis on Blake, and then by chance I taught a combination

00:01:45.560 --> 00:01:55.400
 of courses, mostly biology, but a painting course or two at a little college in Urbana,

00:01:55.400 --> 00:01:56.800
 Ohio.

