 So I taught linguistics at Montana State for a year and tried to restart Blake College

00:02:38.200 --> 00:02:40.760
 in Oregon.

00:02:40.760 --> 00:02:51.080
 That went on for a couple of years with the FBI constantly watching the students and such.

00:02:51.080 --> 00:02:57.680
 And then I went to graduate school in 1968 at the University of Oregon.

00:02:57.680 --> 00:03:10.400
 And I had been studying in relation to language and Blake's ideas, theory of knowledge.

00:03:10.400 --> 00:03:17.920
 I had been thinking about concentrating on brain physiology, but at the university I

00:03:17.920 --> 00:03:28.560
 found that that was the most dogmatic area in the biology department other than genetics.

00:03:28.560 --> 00:03:40.360
 Biological theory was sort of a caricature of primitive computer theory at the time.

