 So I found a really physiological area of biology that was reproductive and aging physiology.

00:03:49.120 --> 00:03:55.080
 That's what I did my thesis on.

00:03:55.080 --> 00:04:03.360
 And since then I've just been following up similar ideas, both in theory of knowledge

00:04:03.360 --> 00:04:12.800
 and function of the brain and how the reproductive hormones, for example, affect the brain function.

