 Linguistics, when Blake College was shut down, I thought I would just simply shift my activity

00:15:27.640 --> 00:15:31.840
 to teaching linguistics.

00:15:31.840 --> 00:15:45.800
 I saw that the influence of Chomsky with Pentagon funding had spread across the country by the

00:15:45.800 --> 00:15:49.160
 late 1960s.

00:15:49.160 --> 00:15:54.200
 It was getting into essentially every department of the humanities.

00:15:54.200 --> 00:16:03.480
 I taught a course through the Honors College at the University of Oregon on interdepartmental

00:16:03.480 --> 00:16:07.840
 conceptions of human nature.

